{"comments":"ASC Color Decision List (CDL) for Professional Color Grading.\n\n**INDUSTRY STANDARD COLOR CORRECTION:**\nCDL is the American Society of Cinematographers' standard for\ncommunicating color correction information between software.\n\n**The CDL Formula:**\n```\nout = (in × slope + offset) ^ power\n```\n\n**Components:**\n- `Slope` - Multiplier (gain/contrast) per channel\n- `Offset` - Addition (lift/brightness) per channel\n- `Power` - Exponent (gamma) per channel\n- `Saturation` - Global saturation multiplier\n\n**Why CDL?**\n- Universal exchange between DaVinci, Baselight, Mistika, etc.\n- Mathematically invertible\n- Non-destructive metadata\n- Shot-by-shot corrections in EDL/XML workflows\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CDL"],"CDL"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[235,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[235,1]},"title":"eqCDL"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CDL"],"CDL"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[238,39],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[237,1]},"title":"showCDL"}],"comments":"Complete ASC CDL specification\n\nContains:\n- Per-channel Slope, Offset, Power (SOP)\n- Global Saturation\n- Metadata for workflow integration\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[233,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[229,1]},"title":"CDL"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CDL"],"Slope"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[112,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[112,1]},"title":"eqSlope"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CDL"],"Slope"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[115,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"showSlope"}],"comments":"Slope (multiplier) - 0.0 to 4.0\n\nThe slope multiplies the input value. A slope of 1.0 is neutral.\n- < 1.0: Reduces intensity\n- > 1.0: Increases intensity (contrast)\nRange is 0.0-4.0 per ASC CDL specification.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[110,29],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[110,1]},"title":"Slope"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CDL"],"Offset"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[134,1]},"title":"eqOffset"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CDL"],"Offset"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[137,40],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[136,1]},"title":"showOffset"}],"comments":"Offset (addition) - -1.0 to 1.0\n\nThe offset is added after slope multiplication. An offset of 0.0 is neutral.\n- < 0.0: Darkens image (lifts blacks)\n- > 0.0: Brightens image (lifts blacks)\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[132,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[132,1]},"title":"Offset"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CDL"],"Power"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[156,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[156,1]},"title":"eqPower"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CDL"],"Power"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[159,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[158,1]},"title":"showPower"}],"comments":"Power (exponent) - 0.1 to 4.0\n\nThe power raises the result to this exponent. A power of 1.0 is neutral.\n- < 1.0: Lifts midtones (gamma up)\n- > 1.0: Darkens midtones (gamma down)\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,29],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/CDL.purs","start":[154,1]},"title":"Power"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":